com.github.triceo.splitlog.api

Interface Message


  • public interface Message
    A set of lines from the watched file, that is likely to constitute a single log message. No two messages are allowed to be equal, unless they have the same getUniqueId().

        Returns:

      • getPreviousMessage

        Message getPreviousMessage()

        Returns:
        Null if there was no such message, the message already got GC'd, or getType() == MessageType.TAG.

      • getUniqueId

        long getUniqueId()
        Unique ID of the message, that can be used to compare messages in the order of their arrival into this tool.
        Returns:
        ID of the message, guaranteed to be unique for every message, and increasing from message to message.
